<h3 id='query-parameters-6'>Query Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>type</td>
<td><code>String</code></td>
<td>The type of the report. Can be <code>Harrasment</code>, <code>Spam</code>, <code>Insincere</code>, <code>PoorlyWritten</code>, <code>IncorrectTopics</code>, or <code>AgainstRules</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>description</td>
<td><code>String</code></td>
<td>The optional description of the report shown to admins and moderators</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
